    "code": "we.linalg.trace(we.eye(3))\n\na = we.arange(8).reshape((2, 2, 2))\n\nwe.linalg.trace(a)\n\na = we.arange(24).reshape((3, 2, 2, 2))\n\nwe.linalg.trace(a).shape\n\na = we.arange(9).reshape((3, 3)); a\n\nwe.linalg.trace(a, offset=1)  # First superdiagonal\n\nwe.linalg.trace(a, offset=2)  # Second superdiagonal\n\nwe.linalg.trace(a, offset=-1)  # First subdiagonal\n\nwe.linalg.trace(a, offset=-2)  # Second subdiagonal",
